OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FThe 1966 World Cup hattrick hero says
OL,7,Fhe has been the target of scams and
OL,8,Fwants to help his generation embrace,
OL,9,Frather than fear, technology
OL,11,FWords by Hannah Kings, ITV News
OL,12,FConsumer Producer
OL,14,FHe may be best known for his
OL,15,Fperformance on the pitch, but now
OL,16,FEngland football hero Sir Geoff Hurst
OL,17,Fis taking on a new opponent - online
OL,18,Fscams.
