OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FResearch by BT Group shows that over a
OL,7,Fquarter (28%) of people over 65
OL,8,Freceive multiple scam calls, texts or
OL,9,Femails a week, with those aged 55 to
OL,10,F64 encountering more scams than any
OL,11,Fother age group.
OL,13,FNow, the star striker is urging his
OL,14,Fpeers to kick out the conmen by
OL,15,Flearning digital skills and educating
OL,16,Fthemselves about some of the most
OL,17,Fcommon tactics fraudsters use.
