OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FSir Geoff tells ITV News: "I'm one of
OL,7,Fthe people that they're targeting
OL,8,Fbecause of my nervousness when I come
OL,9,Fanywhere near a computer or something
OL,10,FI can't work. Life has changed
OL,11,Fdramatically in the digital world in
OL,12,Fthe last 20 years".
OL,14,F"I've been targeted," he explains. "It
OL,15,Fwas a TV licence. They push you into a
OL,16,Fstage where you think you have to do
OL,17,Fsomething, and get you worried and
OL,18,Fconcerned. That's part of the wording
OL,19,F- 'I must do it, I must do it'. Stop
OL,20,Fand think".
