OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FWe joined Sir Geoff at a digital
OL,7,Fskills session at Ashton Gate Stadium
OL,8,Fin , where members of Bristol City
OL,9,FFC's senior walking football team were
OL,10,Flearning how to spot and avoid scams.
OL,12,F"I treat everything I get now, almost
OL,13,F- that I'm not sure about - as a
OL,14,Fscam", Sir Geoff tells the group.
OL,16,FTrainers from AbilityNet, a charity
OL,17,Fwhich supports those looking for help
OL,18,Fwith their digital skills, then talked
OL,19,Fthrough a range of common cons, from
OL,20,Fparking scams to false endorsements
OL,21,Fand romance fraud.
