OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FDuring the interactive session, a
OL,7,Fnumber of people said they had been
OL,8,Fthe victim of a scam - and some had
OL,9,Flost considerable amounts of money.
OL,11,FOne of those who put up his hand in
OL,12,Fthe discussion was Colin Knapp. He was
OL,13,Ftargeted by scammers who persuaded him
OL,14,Fthere was something wrong with his
OL,15,Fcomputer, and that he needed to allow
OL,16,Fthem to access it remotely.
