OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FFortunately, Colin was able to call
OL,7,Fhis son for help, and his bank managed
OL,8,Fto stop the scammers before they took
OL,9,Fany money, but he says he still feels
OL,10,Fshaken by the experience.
OL,12,F"The damage that's done - it makes you
OL,13,Fexceedingly vulnerable, and question
OL,14,Feverything you do in your life," Colin
OL,15,Ftells ITV News.
OL,17,F"It's frightening, very frightening.
OL,18,FSuffice to say now I am frightened to
OL,19,Fdeath to touch anything to do with the
OL,20,FIT. I just steer away from it as much
OL,21,Fas I can. And that shouldn't be".
