OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FPhil Summerhayes told us how he lost
OL,7,Fover #300 to a purchasing scam - after
OL,8,Fseeing an advert that appeared to be
OL,9,Fpublicising a special offer from Marks
OL,10,Fand Spencer.
OL,12,F"The site looked incredibly like M&S,
OL,13,Fso I spent #350", he said.
OL,15,FRob McLean was one of the trainers
OL,16,Frunning the session. He was inspired
OL,17,Fto get involved when his mum lost
OL,18,Fthousands to a romance scammer.
