OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,F"I think you have to admire that
OL,7,Fspirit, but I would caution people
OL,8,Fagainst getting embroiled in further
OL,9,Fconversations; risking giving more
OL,10,Finformation. I think drawing a firm
OL,11,Fline under something, ending that
OL,12,Fconversation and moving on is the way
OL,13,Fto go".
OL,15,FAsked how it feels that members of his
OL,16,Fage group have emerged as targets for
OL,17,Fscammers, Sir Geoff says: "It makes
OL,18,Fyou feel sad in a sense that you've
OL,19,Fgot people out there trying to do that
OL,20,Fto - in our age group - very old and
OL,21,Fvery vulnerable people".
