OL,3,CIs it 'all over' for online scammers?
OL,4,CSir Geoff Hurst hopes it will be
OL,6,FOf course, we couldn't spend an
OL,7,Fafternoon with Sir Geoff Hurst without
OL,8,Fasking him about that controversial
OL,9,Fsecond World Cup goal. So, was it
OL,10,Freally in?
OL,12,FSir Geoff's verdict - delivered with
OL,13,Fthe hint of a smile: "Had VAR been
OL,14,Faround in our time, it would have
OL,15,Fshown unequivocally that the ball was
OL,16,Fover the line".
OL,18,FHe goes on to conclude: "After 60
OL,19,Fyears...who cares?"
